    endpoint: '/quickbooks-desktop/date-driven-terms/{id}',
    httpMethod: 'get',
    summary: 'Retrieve a date-driven term',
    description:
      'Retrieves a date-driven term by ID.\n\n**IMPORTANT:** If you need to fetch multiple specific date-driven terms by ID, use the list endpoint instead with the `ids` parameter. It accepts an array of IDs so you can batch the request into a single call, which is significantly faster.',
    stainlessPath: '(resource) qbd.date_driven_terms > (method) retrieve',
