    markdown:
      "## list\n\n`conductor.qbd.templates.list(Conductor-End-User-Id: string): { data: template[]; hasMore: boolean; nextCursor: string; objectType: 'list'; remainingCount: number; url: string; }`\n\n**get** `/quickbooks-desktop/templates`\n\nReturns a list of templates. Use the `cursor` parameter to paginate through the results.\n\n### Parameters\n\n- `Conductor-End-User-Id: string`\n  The ID of the End-User to receive this request.\n\n### Returns\n\n- `{ data: { id: string; createdAt: string; isActive: boolean; name: string; objectType: 'qbd_template'; revisionNumber: string; templateType: string; updatedAt: string; }[]; hasMore: boolean; nextCursor: string; objectType: 'list'; remainingCount: number; url: string; }`\n\n  - `data: { id: string; createdAt: string; isActive: boolean; name: string; objectType: 'qbd_template'; revisionNumber: string; templateType: string; updatedAt: string; }[]`\n  - `hasMore: boolean`\n  - `nextCursor: string`\n  - `objectType: 'list'`\n  - `remainingCount: number`\n  - `url: string`\n\n### Example\n\n```typescript\nimport Conductor from 'conductor-node';\n\nconst client = new Conductor();\n\nconst templates = await conductor.qbd.templates.list({ conductorEndUserId: 'end_usr_1234567abcdefg' });\n\nconsole.log(templates);\n```",
